God's not dead!
He's surely alive!

1693
01:59:16,631 --> 01:59:18,383
You know I'm gonna
need my keys back.

1694
01:59:18,384 --> 01:59:20,135
I know.

1695
01:59:20,168 --> 01:59:22,637
Two days of ice chips.
I'm starving.

1696
01:59:22,671 --> 01:59:25,474
I'm hungry as well,
David.

1697
01:59:25,506 --> 01:59:28,210
How about I take you
