Yes.

1700
01:59:32,113 --> 01:59:34,049
You're under arrest.

1701
01:59:35,417 --> 01:59:36,886
For what?

1702
01:59:36,887 --> 01:59:38,354
Contempt of court.

1703
01:59:38,386 --> 01:59:40,956
You failed to produce your
sermons upon court order.

1704
01:59:40,989 --> 01:59:42,646
Please put your hands
behind your back.

1705
01:59:42,647 --> 01:59:43,391
Please be gentle.

1706
01:59:43,425 --> 01:59:45,661
He's just been released
from the hospital.

1707
01:59:45,694 --> 01:59:47,964
I don't understand. What
is being accused of?

1708
01:59:47,997 --> 01:59:49,699
You have the right
to remain silent.

1709
01:59:49,731 --> 01:59:52,600
Anything you say can and will be
used against you in a court of law.

1710
01:59:52,634 --> 01:59:54,251
You have a right to an attorney.

1711
01:59:54,252 --> 01:59:56,972
If you cannot afford an attorney,
one will be provided.

1712
01:59:57,006 --> 02:00:00,610
Do you understand the rights I
have just read to you? -Yes.

1713
02:00:07,248 --> 02:00:08,617
Sorry about this,
Pastor.

1714
02:00:08,649 --> 02:00:11,186
It's okay.

1715
02:00:11,220 --> 02:00:14,190
Looks like I'm gonna need you to fill
in for me a little while longer.

1716
02:00:14,222 --> 02:00:16,725
Of course, David.
Anything you need.

1717
02:00:22,030 --> 02:00:24,367
What do we do now?

1718
02:00:24,399 --> 02:00:26,101
Same as always,
Martin.

1719
02:00:26,135 --> 02:00:28,704
We pray, in faith.

